    "In particular, the RL system has a state vector containing hip and knee joint angular position and velocities and the action is selected via an actor-critic system.",
    "The effectiveness of the controller is tested through simulations using an exoskeleton walk-assisting device model, returning angular error ≤ 0.08 rad for both the tested DoFs.",
    "In particular, is used RWAD developed in the SimMechanics toolbox (Matlab/Simulink).",
    "Xu et al. (2020) proposed a master-slave exoskeletal system for mirror therapy to transfer therapeutic training from the patient's functional limb to the impaired limb using a wearable robot in Xu et al. (2020).",
    "The IL mimics the action prescribed by the FL with the assistance of the exoskeleton, stimulating and strengthening developed an exoskeleton with magnetorheological actuators, and clinical experiments were conducted using the proposed system to verify the performance of the framework."
